h4. Actor:
Director, Project Director, Chief Financial Officer.

h4. Description:
User will see all Budget Line Item within the system under following columns:
# Serial (Default: Invisible)
# Item
# Budget Quantity
# Budget Amount (Sum of Budget Item Quantity * Estimated Cost)
# Consume Quantity (Approved)
# Consume Amount (Approved Item Quantity * Rate)

h4. Pre-condition:
# Show only Budget Line Item Consumption list.
# Show only Approved Consumption List here.
# Listed Item must be unique.

h4. Process:
Get list of Consumption Deviation from server (default: 20 at Max).

